  "secondName": "Bearer of the Demon Maul",
  "description": "But Vonn's heroics soon came to an end. One stormy night, the forces of the Pandemonium laid siege to Vonn's home itself. Vonn eagerly joined the fray against them with his maul, and it didn't take long for him to crush all of the attacking forces.\n\nAt that moment, the demon in the maul intentionally loosened his grip on the boy's mind, so that he could see what had really transpired. There was no siege, there were no Aeon Knights... Only his beloved family, who now lay dead and broken throughout the castle.\n\nAs the truth dawned on Vonn, his mind shattered, allowing the demon to fully claim his soul.",
